rt displaying results.'=>'Please allow Google Analytics 24 hours to start displaying results.','Checkout Process Initiated'=>'Checkout Process Initiated','Product Detail Views'=>'Product Detail Views','Product Clicks from Listing Pages'=>'Product Clicks from Listing Pages','Product Impressions from Listing Pages'=>'Product Impressions from Listing Pages','Remove from Cart Events'=>'Remove from Basket Events','Add to Cart Events'=>'Add to Basket Events','This requires a payment gateway that redirects to the thank you/order received page after payment. Orders paid with gateways which do not do this will not be tracked.'=>'This requires a payment gateway that redirects to the thank you/order received page after payment. Orders paid with gateways which do not do this will not be tracked.','Purchase Transactions'=>'Purchase Transactions','Set the Google Analytics code to support Display Advertising. %1$sRead more about Display Advertising%2$s.'=>'Set the Google Analytics code to support Display Advertising. %1$sRead more about Display Advertising%2$s.','"Display Advertising" Support'=>'"Display Advertising" Support','Google Analytics for WooCommerce'=>'Google Analytics for WooCommerce','Allows Google Analytics tracking code to be inserted into WooCommerce store pages.'=>'Allows Google Analytics tracking code to be inserted into WooCommerce store pages.','https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-google-analytics-integration/'=>'https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-google-analytics-integration/','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','Google Analytics is a free service offered by Google that generates detailed statistics about the visitors to a website.'=>'Google Analytics is a free service offered by Google that generates detailed statistics about the visitors to a website.','Google Analytics'=>'Google Analytics']];